subtitle  856 This Is an Improvement over my 7:07 Run.
subtitle  1703 The bottom of the Flagpole makes you lose time because Mario sort of brushes on the Flagpole block, in a walkathon going on the bottom of the flagpole Is your only choice.
subtitle  9708 I used more than 3 bumps because 3 bumps doesen't work.
subtitle  13660 Goomba Jump Is used because Mario can't Jump over the cliff.
subtitle  17553 Another enemy jump because Mario Can't even get close to jumping over the cliff.
subtitle  23987 Wrong warp pipe Is not used because the plant comes out too early.
subtitle  25425 Wall jump Is used because this Is another jump that mario cannot make.

